=head1 NAME

squid_requests - Plugin to monitor squid requests.

=head1 CONFIGURATION

Configuration variables:

 squidhost   - host (default "localhost")
 squidport   - port (default "3128")
 squiduser   - username (default "")
 squidpasswd - password (default "")

